  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<blockquote type=\"cite\">As of August 31, 2025, hotfixes for Liferay DXP 7.4 Updates 1-91 are no longer available*. This is in accordance with the policy previously announced in this article: <a data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\" href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/quarterly-release-transitional-support-coverage\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" url=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/quarterly-release-transitional-support-coverage\">Quarterly Release Transitional Support Coverage</a>.<br>\n<br>\nHotfixes will continue to be available for Liferay DXP 7.4 Update 92 until Sept 1, 2027.<br>\n<br>\n<b>Additional Information</b></blockquote>\n\n<ul data-border=\"1\" data-border-radius-bottom-cap=\"0\" data-border-radius-top-cap=\"0\" data-indent=\"0\" data-list-tree=\"true\">\n\t<li><a data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\" href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/quarterly-release-transitional-support-coverage\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" url=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/quarterly-release-transitional-support-coverage\">Quarterly Release Transitional Support Coverage</a></li>\n\t<li><a data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\" href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/liferay-dxp-quarterly-release-process\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" url=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/liferay-dxp-quarterly-release-process\">Liferay DXP Quarterly Release Process</a></li>\n\t<li><a data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\" href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/liferay-dxp-product-delivery-method-1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" url=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/liferay-dxp-product-delivery-method-1\">Liferay DXP 7.4 Product Delivery Method</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n<p>* Liferay may still provide existing hotfixes on the customer's version or recommend updates/upgrades to address product issues</p>"
      },
